name: Minetest 0.4.14
body:
The long-awaited release (it's been 9 months) is finally here. Now with less bugs and more features.
Check the changelog [here](http://dev.minetest.net/Changelog#0.4.13_.E2.86.92_0.4.14).

name: Minetest 0.4.11
body:
Check the changelog [here](http://dev.minetest.net/Changelog#0.4.10_.E2.86.92_0.4.11).

There are no Android or MSVC builds yet, we'll add them soon.

name: Minetest 0.4.10
body: Check the changelog [here](http://dev.minetest.net/Changelog#0.4.9_.E2.86.92_0.4.10). Notes about the Android version: - Most android devices are ARM, try the armeabi version first. - Unzip the android packages prior to installing (GitHub doesn't allow apk files) - Android discussion thread: https://forum.minetest.net/viewtopic.php?f=3&t=9389
